Justice Point Pretrial Services Discharge Report received and filed.
Justice Point Violation Report forwarded to Judge for review and filed.

No Contact Order, signed and filed.

Defendant Asahel S Ali in court with attorney Maryann Corea.  Defendant Asahel S Ali in custody.  Nate K. Mcclure appeared for the State of Wisconsin.
